"{\"uid\": \"oedigital.com-news-510777-outfitting-work-set-to-start-for-olympic-s-csov-built-by-ulstein\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"PublishedJan 15, 2024 5:14 am ET  The first of two methanol-ready newbuild Construction Service Operation Vessels (CSOVs) for the Norwegian shipowner Olympic has arrived at the outfitting yard of Ulstein Verft in Norway.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 220, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 130, \"end\": 139, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\", \"score\": 0.9999999939630015, \"rank\": 5.999863372693402e-09, \"text\": \"Norwegian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\"}, {\"begin\": 196, \"end\": 209, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ulstein_Group\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ulstein Verft\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ulstein_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ulstein_Group\"}, {\"begin\": 213, \"end\": 219, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 7.728163065660397e-13, \"text\": \"Norway\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The contract between Olympic and Ulsteinwas signed in 2022and includes the construction of two CSOVs for offshore wind at Ulstein Verft.\", \"from\": 222, \"to\": 358, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The vessels are based on the ULSTEIN SX222 design, and have a length of 89.6 meters with a beam of 19.2 meters.\", \"from\": 360, \"to\": 471, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The CSOVs are able to accommodate 126 people in 91 cabins.\", \"from\": 472, \"to\": 530, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The vessels are powered by diesel-electric propulsion with variable speed and large battery energy storage systems.\", \"from\": 532, \"to\": 647, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ulstein Power & Control has been contracted to deliver an extended power and automation package, including a large battery supply, while the Crist yard in Poland is in charge of hulls construction.\", \"from\": 648, \"to\": 845, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 803, \"end\": 809, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland\", \"score\": 0.9647721784849882, \"rank\": 0.02215782342888966, \"text\": \"Poland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Earlier in January 2024, the fist CSOV arrived at Ulstein Verft.\", \"from\": 847, \"to\": 911, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It will be positioned in the dock hall, after which the outfitting work will begin, Ulstein said.\", \"from\": 912, \"to\": 1009, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 996, \"end\": 1003, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ulstein\", \"score\": 0.9997500378454437, \"rank\": 0.00025002465115321235, \"text\": \"Ulstein\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ulstein\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ulstein\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The general outfitting work in the months ahead consists of accommodation work, electrical installations, piping and mechanical installations, to name a few.\", \"from\": 1011, \"to\": 1169, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The vessel will undergo paint work whilst located inside the controlled environment of the dock hall.\", \"from\": 1170, \"to\": 1271, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The commissioning and testing will be executed during the final months of the project,\\\" said project manager Helge Torvik at Ulstein Verft.\", \"from\": 1272, \"to\": 1411, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1397, \"end\": 1410, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ulstein_Group\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ulstein Verft\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ulstein_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ulstein_Group\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We eagerly anticipate the realization of this state-of-the-art offshore wind service vessel, showcasing our commitment to cutting-edge technology and sustainable operations,\\\" added Marius Bergseth COO of Olympic.\", \"from\": 1413, \"to\": 1626, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1595, \"end\": 1601, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaius_Marius\", \"score\": 0.9999948423884453, \"rank\": 5.058411903960779e-06, \"text\": \"Marius\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaius_Marius\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaius_Marius\"}, {\"begin\": 1611, \"end\": 1614, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chief_operating_officer\", \"score\": 0.9999982485514342, \"rank\": 1.7514515611648667e-06, \"text\": \"COO\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chief_operating_officer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chief_operating_officer\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bergseth noted the CSOVs feature the innovative design of the '4-wheel drive system', as one of many innovations highlighting the vessels ability to reduce fuel consumption during dynamic positioning, contributing to its operational efficiency.\", \"from\": 1628, \"to\": 1872, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"With a focus on environmental sustainability, the vessels are not only prepared for methanol fuel but also have the flexibility for additional battery capacity, moving us towards a greener and more emission-conscious maritime future and making this vessel fully compliant to meet the commitment with the Paris agreement,\\\" concluded Bergseth.\", \"from\": 1874, \"to\": 2216, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2179, \"end\": 2194, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris_Agreement\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris agreement\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris_Agreement\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris_Agreement\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The delivery of the vessel is scheduled for the summer of 2024.\", \"from\": 2218, \"to\": 2281, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00a9 2025 AtCoMedia.\", \"from\": 2283, \"to\": 2300, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Inc\", \"from\": 2301, \"to\": 2304, \"entities\": []}]}"